article.title: November 2012 Galaxy Update
article.content:
The November 2012 Galaxy Update is now available.

Highlights:

  • 44 new papers, and 500 total papers in the Galaxy CiteULike group.
  • Galaxy's new issue reporting system
  • Upcoming Events and Deadlines
  • Open Positions at five different institutions
  • Tool Shed Contributions
  • New Distributions
  • Other News

If you have anything you would like to see in the December Galaxy Update, please let us know.

Dave Clements and the Galaxy Team
